    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that requires absolutely no investment or correction.",
