    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and a few small dings, but it is structurally sound with only minor surface rust. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of wear and there are some minor electrical quirks, such as a temperamental radio. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need some routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
      "price": 18500.0,
