    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and a commanding road presence. It exhibits a well-preserved aesthetic and mechanical integrity, having undergone a thorough professional assessment to ensure peak performance. The interior remains refined and comfortable, while the drivetrain delivers the consistent, smooth power delivery expected of a premium pre-owned selection. This offering represents a sophisticated balance of longevity and prestige for the discerning collector or daily commuter.",
