    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
