      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. It is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential for precise torque vectoring. This unit has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and longitudinal dynamics are exceptionally sharp.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
